  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Reason for increase in price of biscuits",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Manufacturers of domestically produced biscuits and sweets have attributed the allegations to price hikes of their products.",
        "They said the prices of many products have been increased as a result of the import of 'A' grade wheat flour for production amid the dollar crisis.",
        "The price of wheat flour was Rs 74 in May and now it is seen at Rs 290-300. This is a 277 percent price hike, according to local manufacturers. (a)"
      ],
